---
title: Middle Eastern Beef & Crumbly Cheese Meatballs with Couscous Tabbouleh & Lemon Yoghurt Dressing
description: Get a load of this meal that's brimming with colour and flavour. With a herb-packed couscous, mildly spiced beef meatballs and a creamy lemon yoghurt dressing, all the elements come together for a delightful explosion of taste!

